CINQ Technologies is a CMMI level 3 certified global company, that provides innovative solutions, mission critical software projects and IT Services; with 26 years of experience developing solutions with cutting-edge technology. CINQ has 15 years of experience in IT Offshore Services.
CINQ also has 10 years of Agile culture, has been elected for 7 consecutive years as one of the best companies to work for by Great Place to Work Institute and is among the TOP 200 SMBs (small and  medium business) that grow more in Brazil (Research by Deloitte and Exame Magazine – 2008, 2009, 2010, 2014, 2018).
Service Offerings:
- Software Solutions Design;
- Agile Software Development;
- Software Testing;
- Agile Outsourcing;
- Offshore Outsourcing.
 
